#. Translators: the label of a message box dialog.
#: addon\installTasks.py:34
msgid "The date and time format you were using are not compatible with this version of the Clock add-on, this will be fixed during installation. Click OK to confirm these corrections"
msgstr "Format datuma i vremena koji ste koristili nije kompatibilan sa ovom verzijom dodatka Sat, ovo će biti ispravljeno tokom instalacije. Kliknite OK da potvrdite ove izmene"

